q=g.hv("Client and Professional Responsibilities","1. Accurate Information: You agree to provide accurate descriptions of the services required or provided.\n\n2. Personal Safety & Environment: You are solely responsible for your own safety and the safety of those around you. Upserv is not responsible for anything that happens during the period of a project.\n\n3. Timely Payments: You agree to make or process payments as agreed upon through the platform's secure systems.\n\n4. Identity Verification: You agree to provide a valid government-issued ID solely for the purpose of verifying your account to prevent duplicate accounts and ensure platform safety.",b,d.bB(e?B.r:B.av))
p=g.hv("Prohibited Actions","Users may not use the platform for any illegal activities, harassment, or to circumvent the platform's payment systems.",b,d.bB(e?B.r:B.av))
o=g.hv("Limitation of Liability","Upserv acts as a facilitator. All users are responsible for their own safety. Upserv is not liable for any incidents, accidents, or outcomes of the work performed. The contract for service is between the client and the professional.",b,d.bB(e?B.r:B.av))
n=g.hv("Account Deletion and Termination","You may request the deletion of your account at any time through the application settings. Upon request, your account will enter a 14-day grace period during which your data remains on our servers but your access is disabled. After this 14-day period, your account and all associated personal data will be permanently and irreversibly deleted from our systems.",b,d.bB(e?B.r:B.av))
m=A.bA("Privacy Policy",f,f,f,f,f,f,f,c,f,f,f)
l=g.hv("Introduction","At Upserv, we value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal data in accordance with the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) and the Protection of Personal Information Act (POPIA).",b,d.bB(e?B.r:B.av))
k=g.hv("Information We Collect","1. Personal Information: We collect information you provide, such as your name, email address, phone number, and physical addresses where services are requested.\n\n2. Usage Data: We collect data about how you interact with our app, including your location (to help find nearby professionals) and device information.\n\n3. Payment Information: We process payments through secure third-party providers and do not store full credit card details on our servers.\n\n4. Identity Documents: We collect government-issued ID documents strictly for account verification purposes to ensure a safe environment. We do not associate ID numbers with names in our databases.",b,d.bB(e?B.r:B.av))
j=g.hv("How We Use Your Information","1. Service Delivery: To connect clients with qualified professionals and facilitate project management.\n\n2. Trust & Safety: To maintain a safe environment by verifying accounts and facilitating reviews.\n\n3. Communication: To send project updates, invoices, and important support messages.",b,d.bB(e?B.r:B.av))
i=g.hv("Information Sharing","We do not sell your personal data. We share your information with:\n\n- Service professionals you choose to hire.\n- Payment processors and other utility providers who help us operate.\n- Legal authorities if required for compliance.",b,d.bB(e?B.r:B.av))
h=g.hv("Your Rights",'Under GDPR and POPIA, you have various rights regarding your personal data, including the right to Access your data, Rectify inaccuracies, Request Erasure ("Right to be Forgotten"), and Withdraw Consent at any time.',b,d.bB(e?B.r:B.av))
